wiki.summary: "Thought You Should Know" is a song by country music singer Morgan Wallen. Released as a promotional single on May 17, 2022, it debuted at #1 on the Billboard Hot Country Songs chart dated for May 21, 2022. The song is Wallen's fourth to debut at the top of that chart. Additionally, it replaced Wallen's "Wasted on You" at the top, making him the first artist to replace himself at the top with a #1 debut. Read more on Last.fm.
